Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.30,0:01:28.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是什么                  - 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瓦斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.39,0:01:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪  会着火的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警报？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.18,0:01:37.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可燃性瓦斯在船内扩散开来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.86,0:01:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.24,0:01:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能关上隔离壁  将瓦斯和那群小鬼一起困住吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.15,0:01:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.34,0:01:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.44,0:01:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对方好像入侵了我们的主机
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的操作一直被封锁着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  连监控都…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的位置和人数都无法得知吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.25,0:01:59.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有他们入侵时的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就放到大屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:04.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.17,0:02:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥…奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.39,0:02:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（现在船内检测到有可燃性瓦斯）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空气净化器  给我好好工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,（警卫以外的人请到指定位置…）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来但丁那边很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是从刚才起  出来的怎么都是女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.91,0:02:29.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过虽然是老招  但还是挺能干的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  那群小鬼是怎么入侵我们系统的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.36,0:02:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我怎么可能知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:41.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥  那不曾经是你家的小鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.20,0:02:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教给那群老鼠什么杂技  我哪能都记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:47.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别管这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请赶紧把他们都杀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可是向名濑先生挑衅了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是抹黑提沃兹的名声了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再  再不快点的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些家伙都要打到这来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请赶紧杀了他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.56,0:03:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请将他们都杀光啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.07,0:03:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得  从刚才起就没什么人抵抗了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,轻轻松松  不正合我们意嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一口气冲向舰桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名濑先生  你有在听我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥  奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.68,0:03:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不清楚这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你已经明白  我们不是一群普通小鬼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.58,0:03:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确  不是一群普通小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  名濑先生  你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是就这么放过这群家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.59,0:03:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那眼神什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  我还有另一件事要办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等下  将你们扔下不管是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:05.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是作战需要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在那里全军覆没的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就一无所有了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.88,0:04:14.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想想是谁一直在照顾你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.22,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们有活干有饭吃的人  到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.46,0:04:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是你啊  马尔巴·艾凯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们一直都听命于你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  我就遵从你的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将他们给…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等  等一下  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:40.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.75,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别被那种家伙的血  脏了自己的手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经见识到你们的觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.03,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就考虑一下和你们交易吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.80,0:04:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  那家伙  只要谈谈还是能懂的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟阿米达联系  说庆典结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦你了  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小孩厮杀  可不是一件有趣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真是一群有前途的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.14,0:07:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.82,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.17,0:07:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.65,0:07:13.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  三日月
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是很抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.58,0:07:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你勉强开这种没调整完毕的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不怪大叔啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.35,0:07:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果呢  最后怎样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:29.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在奥尔加带着大小姐和比斯凯特去洽谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.81,0:07:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定把马尔巴扔去我们的资源采掘卫星了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.42,0:07:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他欠的钱  就用他的身体劳动来偿还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经交给你们了  就拜托你们处理了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.91,0:07:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  这艘船上只看到女性船员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这里是我的后宫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.23,0:07:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这艘船的船员  全都是我的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是您的夫人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就是这么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.11,0:08:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外大概还有五个孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.71,0:08:15.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然都是我的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过母亲是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那种无聊的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是在谈工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  确实
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们的力量我是见识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  你们想要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我们想…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.60,0:08:40.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这位克迪莉娅·蓝那·博斯坦汀小姐送往地球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.04,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  我们需要一个能确保航路安全的向导
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想拜托你们的就是向导这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.08,0:08:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外还有一个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.98,0:08:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否让我们铁华团加入提沃兹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.61,0:08:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加拉尔号角一直追着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.98,0:09:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  提沃兹能成为你们抵抗他们的后盾吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.54,0:09:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟老头子传个话的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十分感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.67,0:09:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能加入还不一定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:24.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是搭个桥  让你们能和老头子交涉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就看你们自己的了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟您的父亲交涉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.87,0:09:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 哈哈  不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是指提沃兹的老大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马克马德·巴里斯通先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  您有说什么要确认克迪莉娅小姐的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.07,0:09:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是说什么资产来着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.86,0:09:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个应该说到什么程度呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对于加拉尔号角是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加拉尔号角吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:10:00.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是军队吗  我不是很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:03.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,300年前  某组织结束了厄祭战
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后以强大的军事力量为后盾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不让战争发生  而从外部监视四个经济圈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:13.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是加拉尔号角
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们开始让各个经济圈感到压力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟最近的加拉尔号角都在追求自家利益了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.38,0:10:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后在那种时候  这位小姐就出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.07,0:10:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「诺亚奇兹的七月会议」上的克迪莉娅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.50,0:10:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织火星独立运动的时代女杰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.31,0:10:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地方上的独立运动家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.88,0:10:44.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越过加拉尔号角  独自与地球经济圈的首领进行会谈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果谈成了  事情就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那必然会动摇加拉尔号角的支配体制
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我没听太懂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正就是个很厉害的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.28,0:11:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和资产究竟有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的去问老头子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说白了就是  这位小姐可不是我这种人能应付的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.68,0:11:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好  大家都没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这多亏了昭弘
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很有本事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是被打得很狼狈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被打得更惨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.56,0:11:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  三日月  你不多吃点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  我饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才吃了平常的一半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  三日月先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.62,0:11:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加先生他们回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说现在在舰桥上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去跟他说  我要去吊架给大叔帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.27,0:11:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边就交给他了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:12:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要去和提沃兹的老大  马克马德·巴里斯通先生交涉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.95,0:12:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先别急
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不代表我们一定能加入提沃兹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.38,0:12:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我们要和塔宾斯一起前往「岁星」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,岁星
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是提沃兹大本营的一艘大船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说现在就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:23.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.61,0:12:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和火星联系上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  告诉他们这边的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.66,0:12:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边好像发来了一封邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.28,0:12:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到火星的运转资金已经快耗尽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.55,0:12:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为能再坚持一下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.27,0:12:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被加拉尔号角盯着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没办法认真做生意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.69,0:12:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.77,0:12:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们聊完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.53,0:12:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们决定要带着那些孩子们回岁星了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘在白色家伙上的那孩子也会来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶员好像不在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.14,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很在意他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我热血沸腾到那种程度的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  他比不上亲爱的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.27,0:13:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过真是一群有趣的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明如果接受名濑的提案  就能轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我说了那边要小心点的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:26.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.93,0:13:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边还有备用的零件  所以还过得去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:42.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.64,0:13:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说事情很顺利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  算是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.09,0:13:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三日你也做得很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.88,0:13:56.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这回没能帮上什么忙  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.86,0:13:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:13:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做的已经够多了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  光凭那样是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要更努力一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:16.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要更加努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说  还没到那个岁星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出发到现在都十天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说快要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 话说  最近都没看到三日月先生呢          - 嘁  昨天也是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 他啊  据说和昭弘先生一起               - 到底什么时候才到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.41,0:14:36.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边的船上用模拟器进行特训啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.54,0:14:38.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  特训吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这两个人明明都那么厉害了  还这么努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相对的这边…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那里有那么多女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.59,0:14:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么就没一个为我所动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁  那种事情怎样都好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.18,0:14:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为全都是名濑先生的夫人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.51,0:14:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是理所当然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.80,0:15:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说这种事情无所谓啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.32,0:15:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,资产…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指我吗  到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.24,0:15:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么提沃兹会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,克迪莉娅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.66,0:15:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待会儿要不要一起去那边的船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那边是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔宾斯那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.83,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  要重新说的是什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在火星从加拉尔号角缴获的物品的清单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:39.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还挺多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:42.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们要说的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望您给我们介绍一些能贩卖这些的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.26,0:15:48.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们没有熟悉的业内人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有从CGS时代就相识的业内人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但毕竟是这种货物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通的业内人应该无法消化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那也是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:01.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  我们会支付相应的介绍费
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能拜托您吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.76,0:16:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们就那么缺钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.89,0:16:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我们很缺钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.01,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那为什么我说给你们介绍工作时  你们拒绝了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.41,0:16:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不是  因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您说如果我们接受了  就要四散各方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.59,0:16:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.83,0:16:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不能分开的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能分开？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真恶心啊  明明都是男人还黏在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便您怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…铁华团是无法分离的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说是为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:48.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.33,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是连在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.03,0:16:55.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牺牲了的同伴所流的血
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.69,0:17:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与今后我们所流的血混在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如铁一般地凝固了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们是无法分离的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.39,0:17:09.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不能分离的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是危险或是痛苦  我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将枪指向马尔巴时  你说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:19.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.27,0:17:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我遵从你的命令  将他们给…」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「他们」是指那些死去的同伴们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法分离  这一点倒是不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:36.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊  如果要一直守护铁华团的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:40.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后谁都不会来指示你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:43.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们会因为你的一声令下而赴死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个责任也不能推给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.00,0:17:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为团长的你  能独自承担起这个责任吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.92,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  这里的孩子全都是名濑先生的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  虽然母亲都各不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有精力吧  我家亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里的只有较小的孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有别的孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.43,0:18:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大一点的都去陆地的学校上学了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.90,0:18:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥他们不在  大家很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.31,0:18:27.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们的家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  好香啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.42,0:18:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.95,0:18:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.97,0:18:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.79,0:18:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为克迪莉娅小姐最近一直愁眉紧锁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.79,0:18:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿特拉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:51.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:55.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经做好觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.01,0:19:02.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想再因为毫不相干的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下达不合理的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.13,0:19:08.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而害同伴们白白牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们的赴死之地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.18,0:19:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要由作为铁华团团长的我来制造
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.54,0:19:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.21,0:19:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的赴死之地也一样如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了他们  我随时可以去死…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥  奥尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.51,0:19:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你死了该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.76,0:19:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了指挥官  铁华团才会变得四分五裂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  血肉相连…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种关系可不是伙伴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是家人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  你们要说的我都明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.62,0:19:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让你们吃亏的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那就拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.67,0:20:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.39,0:20:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:13.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  他不是说会考虑一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题不在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明谈生意必须要双方对等的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却完全被当成孩子来对待了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.73,0:20:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都会相信你并跟随你的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:49.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  赢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.50,0:20:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别闹啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.27,0:20:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太热血可是赢不了的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我会再好好疼爱你的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.25,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 那接下来由我来                   - 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 话说你们啊                  - 等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日复一日的  真的很努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:11.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说  能做的只有这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.67,0:21:17.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在模拟器上是没有阿赖耶识的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我尽情地疼爱你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.75,0:21:25.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个叫奥尔加的孩子  跟你说了什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是些稚气未脱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:30.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得我都不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.37,0:21:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前的你不也是如此嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想回忆往事的话  让我们在床上聊到天亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  捕捉到岁星的正面了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好像就是岁星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.38,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.56,0:21:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也要训练吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.39,0:21:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在那边船上被严格训练着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.20,0:22:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不被奥尔加抛弃  我必须要努力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.73,0:22:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.65,0:22:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于家人来说…没有什么抛不抛弃的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.23,0:22:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.81,0:22:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  三日
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.86,0:22:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  我们是家人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.68,0:24:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团长是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  三日月先生是我的大哥对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.81,0:24:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.31,0:24:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那超强超帅的大哥是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.74,0:24:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.19,0:24:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.98,0:24:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会比过去更努力三倍！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.42,0:24:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集  机动战士高达  铁血的孤儿
